Usage: delete_gui_object [-help] [-shape | -text | -marker | -all | -selected ]

-help      # Prints out the command usage
-all       # All Gui Objects (bool, optional)
-marker    # Gui Markers (bool, optional)
-selected  # Selected Gui Objects (bool, optional)
-shape     # Gui Shapes (bool, optional)
-text      # Gui Texts (bool, optional)